---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="AI Consulting — Nick Dahlhoff" description="I help small businesses in West Michigan figure out where AI and better systems can save them time and money. On-site, hands-on, built around your reality.">
  <div class="page">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="hero-text">
        <h1>Your business has problems technology can solve. I'll find them and fix them.</h1>
        <p class="hero-sub">I'm Nick Dahlhoff — AI &amp; business systems specialist in the Grand Rapids area. Things are changing fast. I help business owners cut through the noise, figure out what new technology actually means for their business, and build the systems to take advantage of it.</p>
        <a href="#contact" class="hero-cta">Tell Me About Your Business</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-photo">
        <img src="/images/nick-headshot.png" alt="Nick Dahlhoff" class="headshot" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Pain Points -->
    <section class="pain-section">
      <div class="pain-grid">
        <div class="pain-card">
          <h3 class="pain-title">Flying Blind</h3>
          <p class="pain-text">Your systems are held together with duct tape and spreadsheets. Your CRM doesn't talk to your invoicing. Your data lives in six different places. You're making important decisions based on gut feeling because getting the real numbers takes too long — or nobody knows where they are. It doesn't have to be this way.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <h3 class="pain-title">Drowning in Busywork</h3>
          <p class="pain-text">You and your team spend hours every week on repetitive tasks that a good system could handle in seconds. Data entry, scheduling, follow-up emails, report generation, copying information from one place to another. It's not the hard work that's killing productivity — it's the busywork.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <h3 class="pain-title">Technology Finally Works for You</h3>
          <p class="pain-text">A professional website, custom software, or polished customer experience used to require a big budget and a dev team. That's changed. New tools make it fast and affordable to build exactly what your business needs — a booking system, a customer portal, a site that actually represents what you do. Most businesses haven't caught on yet.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="pain-card">
          <h3 class="pain-title">Every Business Is Different</h3>
          <p class="pain-text">Your business isn't a template. Generic advice doesn't cut it. I come to your office, walk your floor, follow you through your day, and figure out specifically where technology can make the biggest difference for how YOUR business actually works. Not theory — hands-on, in-person, built around your reality.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Why Me -->
    <section class="why-section">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Why Me</h2>
      <div class="why-grid">
        <div class="why-item">
          <span class="why-number">1</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="why-title">AI Expert</h3>
            <p class="why-text">Deep experience using AI across a wide range of business applications — workflow automation, content strategy, data analysis, software development, and more. I've been working at the frontier of what AI can do for businesses since before it was mainstream, and I apply it practically every day.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <span class="why-number">2</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="why-title">Built &amp; Sold a Business</h3>
            <p class="why-text">I built a language learning website from nothing, grew it to over 100,000 monthly visitors with a team of six contributors, and sold it for $960K. I've run marketing, managed teams, negotiated deals, and handled operations. I understand business problems because I've had them.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <span class="why-number">3</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="why-title">I Show Up</h3>
            <p class="why-text">I'll come to your office, travel to your location, and get into the details with you. The best solutions come from seeing how things actually work on the ground — not guessing from a Zoom call.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <span class="why-number">4</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="why-title">One Person, Not an Agency</h3>
            <p class="why-text">You work directly with me. No account managers, no juniors, no handoffs. When you hire me, you get me.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="why-item">
          <span class="why-number">5</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="why-title">Built to Last Without Me</h3>
            <p class="why-text">Everything I build is designed to work independently — you and your team can run it without me being there. I document everything, train your people, and make sure the systems keep running. And if something breaks or you want to expand later, I'm just a message away.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </section>

    <!-- Pricing Card -->
    <section class="pricing-section">
      <div class="pricing-card">
        <span class="pricing-label">On-Site Consulting</span>
        <div class="pricing-amount">
          <span class="pricing-dollar">$</span><span class="pricing-number">750</span>
          <span class="pricing-per">/ day</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="pricing-includes">
          <li>On-site at your location in West Michigan</li>
          <li>Research, planning, and implementation</li>
          <li>Documentation of everything I build or set up</li>
          <li>Training for you and your team</li>
          <li>Follow-up support to make sure it keeps working</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="pricing-note">Ongoing and larger projects available on request.</p>
        <!-- TODO: Wire up to Stripe Payment Link when account is set up -->
        <a href="#contact" class="pricing-cta">Book a Day</a>
      </div>
      <p class="availability-note">Availability is limited — I take on roughly 20 hours of client work per week.</p>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact / CTA -->
    <section class="contact-section" id="contact">
      <h2 class="section-heading">Let's Talk</h2>
      <div class="contact-grid">
        <div class="contact-form-wrap">
          <h3 class="contact-sub">Describe Your Situation</h3>
          <form class="contact-form" id="consultingForm">
            <input type="hidden" name="source" value="general" />
            <!-- Honeypot — hidden from real users, bots fill it in -->
            <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;" aria-hidden="true">
              <input type="text" name="website" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="name">Your name</label>
              <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Jane Smith" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="email">Email <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="jane@yourbusiness.com" required />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="phone">Phone <span class="optional">(optional)</span></label>
              <input type="tel" id="phone" name="phone" placeholder="(616) 555-0123" />
            </div>
            <div class="form-field">
              <label for="message">What's going on? <span class="required">*</span></label>
              <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" placeholder="Tell me about your business and what you're dealing with. The more detail the better. What's frustrating you? What's eating up your time? What do you wish worked better?" required></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="form-submit">Send It Over</button>
            <p class="form-footnote">I'll review what you send and get back to you within 1-2 business days.</p>
          </form>
          <div class="form-success" id="formSuccess">
            <p class="success-message">Got it — I'll be in touch within 1-2 business days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-call-wrap">
          <h3 class="contact-sub">Or Let's Just Talk</h3>
          <p class="call-text">If you'd rather just have a conversation, book a 30-minute call. No pitch, no pressure — just tell me what's going on and I'll let you know if I can help.</p>
          <button
            class="call-cta"
            data-cal-namespace=""
            data-cal-link="nickdahlhoff/30min"
            data-cal-config='{"layout":"month_view"}'
          >Book a 30-Minute Call</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="consulting-footer">
      <span>Nick Dahlhoff</span>
      <span class="footer-sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>West Michigan</span>
      <span class="footer-sep">&middot;</span>
      <a href="mailto:ndahlhoff10@gmail.com">ndahlhoff10@gmail.com</a>
      <span class="footer-sep">&middot;</span>
      <span>&copy; 2026</span>
    </footer>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<!-- Cal.com embed script -->
<script is:inline>
  (function (C, A, L) { let p = function (a, ar) { a.q.push(ar); }; let d = C.document; C.Cal = C.Cal || function () { let cal = C.Cal; let ar = arguments; if (!cal.loaded) { cal.ns = {}; cal.q = cal.q || []; d.head.appendChild(d.createElement("script")).src = A; cal.loaded = true; } if (ar[0] === L) { const api = function () { p(api, arguments); }; const namespace = ar[1]; api.q = api.q || []; if(typeof namespace === "string"){cal.ns[namespace] = cal.ns[namespace] || api;p(cal.ns[namespace], ar);p(cal, ["initNamespace", namespace]);} else p(cal, ar); return;} p(cal, ar); }; })(window, "https://app.cal.com/embed/embed.js", "init");
  Cal("init", "", {origin:"https://cal.com"});
  Cal("ui", {"styles":{"branding":{"brandColor":"#6B8F6B"}}});
</script>

<!-- Form handling -->
<script is:inline>
  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
    var form = document.getElementById('consultingForm');
    var success = document.getElementById('formSuccess');
    var submitBtn = form ? form.querySelector('.form-submit') : null;

    if (form) {
      form.addEventListener('submit', function(e) {
        e.preventDefault();
        if (submitBtn) {
          submitBtn.disabled = true;
          submitBtn.textContent = 'Sending...';
        }

        var data = {
          name: form.elements.name.value || undefined,
          email: form.elements.email.value,
          phone: form.elements.phone.value || undefined,
          message: form.elements.message.value,
          source: form.elements.source.value || 'general',
          website: form.elements.website.value || undefined,
        };

        fetch('https://calculating-platypus-531.convex.site/leads', {
          method: 'POST',
          headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },
          body: JSON.stringify(data),
        })
          .then(function(res) {
            if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Submission failed');
            form.style.display = 'none';
            success.style.display = 'block';
          })
          .catch(function() {
            if (submitBtn) {
              submitBtn.disabled = false;
              submitBtn.textContent = 'Send It Over';
            }
            alert('Something went wrong — please try again or email ndahlhoff10@gmail.com directly.');
          });
      });
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 1240px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 100px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .section-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 60px;
    padding: 80px 0 60px;
    min-height: 70vh;
  }

  .hero-text {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    width: fit-content;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: var(--color-accent-green);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-green-dark);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .hero-photo {
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .headshot {
    width: 280px;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    object-fit: cover;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(44, 36, 24, 0.1);
    display: block;
  }

  /* Pain Points */
  .pain-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .pain-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .pain-card {
    padding: 28px 32px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-left: 5px solid var(--color-accent-green);
    border-radius: 8px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .pain-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .pain-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
  }

  /* Why Me */
  .why-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .why-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .why-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .why-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent-gold);
    line-height: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 32px;
    padding-top: 2px;
  }

  .why-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .why-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
  }

  /* Pricing */
  .pricing-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .pricing-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-green);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 48px 56px;
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 480px;
    width: 100%;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(44, 36, 24, 0.06);
  }

  .pricing-label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
  }

  .pricing-amount {
    margin: 16px 0 28px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 2px;
  }

  .pricing-dollar {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .pricing-number {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 64px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .pricing-per {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  .pricing-includes {
    list-style: none;
    text-align: left;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .pricing-includes li {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    padding-left: 24px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .pricing-includes li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .pricing-note {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .pricing-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 40px;
    background: var(--color-accent-green);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .pricing-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-green-dark);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .availability-note {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 20px;
  }

  /* Contact */
  .contact-section {
    padding: 60px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 48px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .contact-sub {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .contact-form {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 18px;
  }

  .form-field {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .form-field label {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .required {
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
  }

  .optional {
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .form-field input,
  .form-field textarea {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
    outline: none;
  }

  .form-field input:focus,
  .form-field textarea:focus {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(107, 143, 107, 0.12);
  }

  .form-field textarea {
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 120px;
  }

  .form-submit {
    width: fit-content;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: var(--color-accent-green);
    color: #fff;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .form-submit:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-green-dark);
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  .form-footnote {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .form-success {
    display: none;
  }

  .success-message {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--color-accent-green-dark);
    padding: 32px;
    background: rgba(107, 143, 107, 0.08);
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(107, 143, 107, 0.2);
  }

  .call-text {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--color-text-body);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .call-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 14px 32px;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 600;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-green);
    border-radius: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease, transform 0.15s ease;
  }

  .call-cta:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-green);
    color: #fff;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
  }

  /* Footer */
  .consulting-footer {
    padding: 40px 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .consulting-footer a {
    color: var(--color-accent-green);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .consulting-footer a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent-green-dark);
  }

  .footer-sep {
    color: var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .page {
      padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 40px;
    }

    .headshot {
      width: 220px;
      height: 260px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page {
      padding: 0 20px;
    }

    .hero {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 32px;
      padding: 48px 0 40px;
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 32px;
    }

    .hero-photo {
      align-self: center;
    }

    .headshot {
      width: 200px;
      height: 240px;
    }

    .section-heading {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .pain-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .contact-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .pricing-card {
      padding: 36px 28px;
    }

    .pricing-number {
      font-size: 52px;
    }
  }
</style>
